Package com.milk.uberchat.event

Interface Summary
ChannelHolderListener This is the interface for objects that care about ChannelHolderEvents.
ChannelListener This is the interface for objects that care about ChannelEvents.
EntityListener This is the interface for objects that care about EntityEvents.
ErrorListener This is the interface for objects that care about ErrorEvents.
LocusListener This is the interface for objects that care about LocusEvents.
MessageListener This is the interface for objects that care about MessageEvents.
SystemListener This is the interface for objects that care about SystemEvents.
UserListener This is the interface for objects that care about UserEvents.
 

Class Summary
ChannelEvent This is the class for events having to do with activity that takes place on a channel.
ChannelHolderEvent This is the class for events having to do with channels being added and removed from a ChatChannelHolder.
EntityEvent This is the class for events having to do with happenings on a ChatEntity.
ErrorEvent This is the class for events having to do with errors that need to be reported to the user.
LocusEvent This is the class for events having to do with (non-chat-message) happenings at a ChatLocus.
MessageEvent This is the class for events having to do with chat-messages coming in from the host directed toward a particular ChatLocus.
SystemEvent This is the class for events having to do with ChatSystems.
UserBroadcastDetails This class holds the details of a userBroadcast event.
UserEvent This is the class for events having to do with happenings on a ChatUser.
